com.ibm.team.scm.client.events

Interface ILockEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEvent, IWorkspaceEvent

    public interface ILockEvent
extends IWorkspaceEvent
    Generic event type to describe the stream and component lock changes on a workspace connection. This event is not sent for file lock changes.
    Since:
    0.11.0.2 (RTC 6.0.2)
